name: Changeable OBJKT
description:
The design of this OBJKT will change live for all viewers, based on the OBJKT’s wallet history. 

The OBJKT wallet address is tz1ZFiLYJR1Sywsfr5JrSwCZivFNqkgnhVjE

Sending Tez to this address will change the OBJKT’s current composition. 
(A minimum of .1 Tez is recommended to see noticeable change).

*You do not have to be an owner to change the composition, so simply purchasing the OBJKT will not change its composition. Tez must be sent to the OBJKT wallet in order to change the OBJKT design*
